               <msContents>
                  <summary>Fol. i is blank.</summary>
                  <msItem xml:id="ms_i0">
                     <locus from="1v" to="15r">1v-15r</locus>
                     <textLang xml:lang="ar">Arabic</textLang>
                     <title ref="https://betamasaheft.eu/LIT0049IHA#s18IHA">قران, Eleventh ǧuz’ (11/30)</title>
                     <incipit xml:lang="ar">
                        <locus target="#1v">-1v</locus>يعتذرون اليكم اذا رجعتم اليهم قل لا تعتذروا لن نؤمن لكم</incipit>
                     <explicit xml:lang="ar">
                        <locus target="#15r">-15r</locus>وما يعلنون , انه عليم بذت الصدور</explicit>
                     <note>9:94-11:5. Red circles with a central dot as verse markers. On fol. 1v, the ink has seeped through the paper. Ḥizb marker in black on fol. 8v. Corrections, additions. The identification of the scribe is based on note in the end of the waqf text in the present manuscript fol. 1r and a note in ASH00276 (fol. 13r).</note>
                     <note/>
                  </msItem>
